\begin_layout Subsection

\size normal
Clustering Methods:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
There are mainly four types of clustering methods.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
1.
 Partitioning methods
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
2.
 Hierarchical methods
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
3.
 Model-based methods
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
4.
 Density-based methods
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
We use mainly Hierarchical clustering here.
